OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome sunshine in the north and
OL,6,Feast at first. Otherwise a mainly
OL,7,Fcloudy though largely dry day. A
OL,8,Flittle rain developing over southern
OL,9,Fand western Aberdeenshire later.
OL,10,FStrengthening southerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA windy evening with gales
OL,13,Falong the east coast. Outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain turning heavier in south and east
OL,15,Fbut little reaching the north coast.
OL,16,FClearer overnight then showers in west.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FBright or sunny intervals
OL,19,Fand showers, frequent in the west at
OL,20,Ffirst. Strong to gale westerly winds
OL,21,Fslowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
