OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Thursday then sunny intervals
OL,7,Fand blustery showers, Colder Friday
OL,8,Fwith showers wintry at first. Saturday
OL,9,Fbright and breezy with a few showers.
